<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>jiāng cán de dēng huǒ zhǔ cóng bù chuī miè 迦南1311</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 jiāng cán de dēng huǒ zhǔ cóng bù chuī miè yā shāng de lú wěi zhǔ cóng bù zhé duàn
 wǒ yǒng yuǎn jì dé zhǔ duì wǒ shuō guò yǒng bù diū qì wǒ ài wǒ bù biàn
 jiāng cán de dēng huǒ zhǔ cóng bù chuī miè hé děng dà de ān wèi chōng mǎn wǒ xīn jiān
 yā shāng de lú wěi zhǔ cóng bù zhé duàn zhèn zhèn nuǎn liú yǒng jìn wǒ xīn tián
 zhǔ wéi yǒu nǐ shì wǒ de shén nǐ de cí ài zhí dào yǒng yuǎn
 zhǔ wéi yǒu nǐ shì zhěng jiù wǒ de shén wǒ yào bǎ nǐ de míng chuán biàn rén jiān</lyrics>
<hymn_number>1311</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>